<br />I've seen jrlepage's NSF test, and he's explained that the envelopes play at a different speed on VirtuaNSF and NSFPlug, but I have no point of reference for which (if either) is the correct behaviour. (Also it would be nice to have a test that isolates specific features, like the envelope.)
